#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/datasource.adoc:125
msgid "You can also retrieve the password from Vault by link:vault-datasource[using a credential provider] for your datasource."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/datasource.adoc:127
msgid "Once you have defined the database kind and the credentials, you are ready to configure either a JDBC datasource, a reactive one, or both."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/datasource.adoc:132
msgid "JDBC is the most common database connection pattern.  You typically need a JDBC datasource when using Hibernate ORM."
